      "title": "Executive Summary",
      "content": {
        "summary": "The January 2026 financial performance shows a net operating result of $82,500 with total revenue at $2,100,000 and expenses at $2,017,500. All departments met their revenue targets but experienced expense overruns, with payroll being the largest expense category at $798,000 (38% of revenue). The cash flow remains healthy with $150,000 net cash flow and $2,650,000 ending cash.",
